#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.kde.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.plot.kde"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:1
#: of
msgid "Generate Kernel Density Estimate plot using Gaussian kernels."
msgstr "使用高斯核生成核密度估计图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:3
#: of
msgid ""
"In statistics, `kernel density estimation`_ (KDE) is a non-parametric way"
" to estimate the probability density function (PDF) of a random variable."
" This function uses Gaussian kernels and includes automatic bandwidth "
"determination."
msgstr ""
"在统计学中，`核密度估计`_ (KDE) 是一种非参数方法，用于估计随机变量的"
"概率密度函数 (PDF)。 此函数使用高斯核，并包含自动带宽确定功能。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:11
#: of
msgid ""
"The method used to calculate the estimator bandwidth. This can be "
"'scott', 'silverman', a scalar constant or a callable. If None (default),"
" 'scott' is used. See :class:`scipy.stats.gaussian_kde` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"用于计算估计器带宽的方法。可以是 'scott'、'silverman'、标量常数或可调用"
"对象。如果为 None（默认），则使用 'scott'。更多信息请参见 :class:`scipy."
"stats.gaussian_kde`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:16
#: of
msgid ""
"Evaluation points for the estimated PDF. If None (default), 1000 equally "
"spaced points are used. If `ind` is a NumPy array, the KDE is evaluated "
"at the points passed. If `ind` is an integer, `ind` number of equally "
"spaced points are used."
msgstr ""
"用于评估估计 PDF 的点。如果为 None（默认），则使用 1000 个等间距点。如果 "
"`ind` 是 NumPy 数组，则 KDE 会在传入的点上进行评估。如果 `ind` 是整数，则"
"使用 `ind` 个等间距点。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:21
#: of
msgid "Additional keyword arguments are documented in :meth:`DataFrame.plot`."
msgstr "其他关键字参数请参见 :meth:`DataFrame.plot`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner
#: of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:28
#: of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.gaussian_kde`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:29
#: of
msgid ""
"Representation of a kernel-density estimate using Gaussian kernels. This "
"is the function used internally to estimate the PDF."
msgstr "使用高斯核的核密度估计表示。这是内部用于估计 PDF 的函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:32
#: of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.PlotAccessor._gen_func.<locals>._inner:33
#: of
msgid ""
"Given a Series of points randomly sampled from an unknown distribution, "
"estimate its PDF using KDE with automatic bandwidth determination and "
"plot the results, evaluating them at 1000 equally spaced points "
"(default):"
msgstr ""
"给定一个从未知分布中随机采样的点序列，使用 KDE 和自动带宽确定来估计其 PDF"
"，并绘制结果，默认在 1000 个等间距点上进行评估："

